      "correctIndex": 3,
      "explanation_fr": "Arbre pondéré : $P(R_2) = P(R_1)P_{R_1}(R_2) + P(N_1)P_{N_1}(R_2) = \\frac25\\cdot\\frac35 + \\frac35\\cdot\\frac36 = \\frac{6}{25} + \\frac{3}{10} = \\frac{12}{50} + \\frac{15}{50} = \\frac{27}{50}$."
